Our rivers, lakes and ponds 
have become polluted,

00:01:44.568 --> 00:01:48.944
and the air we breathe
is turning into a gas chamber.

00:01:48.968 --> 00:01:53.208
A famous scientist,
Buckminster Fuller, said,

